00:08:12.030 --> 00:08:14.479
When she woke up, Ratner was the only one
in the apartment.

00:08:14.479 --> 00:08:18.490
Henstridge attempted to leave, but Ratner
put himself between her and the door and began

00:08:18.490 --> 00:08:22.559
to touch himself, and then forcing her to
perform oral sex on him.

00:08:22.559 --> 00:08:25.789
Ratner has denied all the allegations, but
that hasn’t stopped him from feeling the

00:08:25.789 --> 00:08:26.789
heat.

00:08:26.789 --> 00:08:30.479
Warner Brothers has cut ties with Ratner’s
production company RatPac and his remaining

00:08:30.479 --> 00:08:33.969
ties with the studio have already started
to raise problems.

00:08:33.969 --> 00:08:34.969
3.

00:08:34.969 --> 00:08:35.969
Steven Seagal

00:08:35.969 --> 00:08:39.620
