who seemed unsurprised by the behavior.

00:08:53.220 --> 00:08:56.200
Jenny Mccarthy has also revealed that she
was harassed by Seagal.

00:08:56.200 --> 00:08:59.690
Auditioning for Under Siege 2, Seagal told
her to take off her dress.

00:08:59.690 --> 00:09:02.730
