pants.

00:09:02.730 --> 00:09:06.490
McCarthy ran out of the room to her car, where
Seagal followed her and told her not to tell

00:09:06.490 --> 00:09:08.130
anyone about the encounter.

00:09:08.130 --> 00:09:09.130
2.

00:09:09.130 --> 00:09:10.270
George Takei

