00:09:16.410 --> 00:09:20.320
A male model has accused Takei of drugging
him and sexually assaulting him more than

00:09:20.320 --> 00:09:21.540
two decades ago.

00:09:21.540 --> 00:09:25.440
Takei’s accuser, Scott R. Brunton, claims
that after he broke up with his boyfriend,

00:09:25.440 --> 00:09:27.620
Takei offered to take him out to dinner.

00:09:27.620 --> 00:09:31.220
After returning to Takei’s home, Brunton
felt tired and disoriented.

00:09:31.220 --> 00:09:33.760
When he woke up, he saw Takei taking off his
