00:09:37.890 --> 00:09:41.780
even after a salacious interview with Howard
Stern surfaced, where Takei discussed fondling

00:09:41.780 --> 00:09:44.100
men without their consent.

00:09:44.100 --> 00:09:45.100
1.

00:09:45.100 --> 00:09:46.100
Ed Westwick

00:09:46.100 --> 00:09:49.150
Like with Andy Dick, maybe “respected”
doesn’t quite fit the bill here.

00:09:49.150 --> 00:09:52.990
But it’s next to impossible to leave this
one off the list, because some of the most

00:09:52.990 --> 00:09:57.470
serious accusations we’re talking about
today have been levied against Gossip Girl

00:09:57.470 --> 00:09:58.780
star Ed Westwick.

00:09:58.780 --> 00:10:03.060
The 30-year-old actor has been accused of
rape and sexual assault by multiple women.

00:10:03.060 --> 00:10:06.580
The separate allegations all have connections
and similarities.

00:10:06.580 --> 00:10:11.480
A producer on Gossip Girl invited both Rachel
Eck and Kristina Cohen to nights out with

00:10:11.480 --> 00:10:14.880
the actor, which ended with them being assaulted
by Westwick.

00:10:14.880 --> 00:10:19.050
The allegations made by Cohen describe the
aspiring actress waking to find Westwick on

00:10:19.050 --> 00:10:20.050
