00:10:20.050 --> 00:10:23.970
Her attempts to fight him off would fail,
and Westwick would allegedly go on to rape

00:10:23.970 --> 00:10:24.970
her.

00:10:24.970 --> 00:10:28.510
Westwick has denied each accusation, releasing
a statement noting his disappointment with

00:10:28.510 --> 00:10:29.910
a rush to judgment.

00:10:29.910 --> 00:10:31.860
He claims to have not even met his accusers.

00:10:31.860 --> 00:10:36.720
Nonetheless, the BBC has canceled the TV show
Ordeal by Innocence, starring Westwick, and

00:10:36.720 --> 00:10:50.230
his series White Gold has been put on hold.

